Pancake - Control your farm via HTTP.

(Still very much in development)

PLUGINS
Pancake::Plugin::HAProxy - http://github.com/robinedwards/Pancake-Plugin-HAProxy
Pancake::Plugin::Env - example, provides information on loaded plugins

CLIENTS
Pancake::Client::HAProxy - http://github.com/robinedwards/Pancake-Client-HAProxy

GETTING STARTED

$ PANCAKE_CONFIG_DIR=/your/plugin_config_dir/ plackup Pancake::Service --port 9999
